                <h1>Who Owns Forbes? Exploring Its Ownership Structure</h1>
                <p>Forbes is owned by Integrated Whale Media Investments, a Hong Kong-based investment group. They acquired a majority stake in the company in 2014, while the Forbes family retains a minority stake and continues to play a role in its operations. Forbes is known worldwide for its lists and rankings including the Forbes 400 and Global 2000.</p>
